5|$|As of 1997, its {{official}} name is the Hong <b>Kong</b> <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> of the People's Republic of China. This {{is the official}} title as mentioned in the Hong Kong Basic Law and the Hong Kong Government's website, but Hong <b>Kong</b> <b>Special</b> <b>Administrative</b> <b>Region</b> and Hong Kong are widely accepted.|$|E
